But the clause  
\( \text{not}(p30) \lor \text{not}(p18) \lor \text{not}(p13) \lor \text{not}(p6) \)  
is then false, because \(p30, p18, p13, p6\) are all forced true, making each negated literal false.

So the set of clauses cannot be satisfied.
